# Architecture constraints

- Controllers handle HTTP only
- Services contain orchestration logic
- Tools perform narrow operations only
- Policy logic lives only in `PolicyEngine`
- Prompt and output guards live in dedicated guard/redaction services
- Repositories only load and persist mock data
- Unsafe and protected agents must remain separate for demo clarity

## Required main services
- `UnsafeAgentService`
- `ProtectedAgentService`
- `LlmOrchestrator`
- `RetrievalService`
- `PolicyEngine`
- `GuardService`
- `ApprovalService`
- `AuditService`
